4 SYNOPSIS:
5 Under existing law, a municipality may regulate
6 the sale of alcoholic beverages on Sunday.
7 This bill would authorize the sale of alcoholic
8 beverages for off-premises consumption in Class 2
9 municipalities on Sunday to commence at 10:00 a.m.
10
11
12 A BILL
13 TO BE ENTITLED
14 AN ACT
15
16 Relating to Class 2 municipalities; to further provide
17 for the sale of alcoholic beverages.
18 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
19 Section 1. In Class 2 municipalities, in addition to
20 any other authority for the sale of alcoholic beverages, the
21 sale of alcoholic beverages for off-premises consumption on
22 Sunday may commence at 10:00 a.m.
23 Section 2. This act shall become effective immediately.
